OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778186666
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a crash in
OL,8,FNewport.
OL,10,FGwent Police is investigating a report
OL,11,Fof a road traffic collision in
OL,12,FAberthaw Road, which reportedly
OL,13,Finvolved a BMW car and a motorbike on
OL,14,FThursday, 7 May.
OL,16,FThe BMW is believed to have left the
OL,17,Fscene before police arrived. Two men -
OL,18,Fthe driver and a passenger of the
OL,19,Fmotorbike - were pronounced dead at
OL,20,Fthe scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
