OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778186666
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FSpecially trained officers will be
OL,7,Fallocated to support the families
OL,8,Fthroughout the investigation.
OL,10,FAn 18-year-old man and a 40-year-old
OL,11,Fwoman were arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Fmurder, while a 24-year-old woman was
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of assisting an
OL,14,Foffender. All three remain in police
OL,15,Fcustody.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
