OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778186666
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FOfficers investigating the
OL,7,Fcircumstances leading up to the
OL,8,Fcollision would like to speak to
OL,9,Fanyone who was travelling along, or
OL,10,Fresidents who reside in, Aberthaw Road
OL,11,Fand the surrounding areas to check
OL,12,Ftheir CCTV, between the hours of
OL,13,Fmidnight and 1:40am on 7 May.
OL,15,FAnyone with information, including
OL,16,FCCTV and dashcam footage, is asked to
OL,17,Fcontact Gwent Police.
